E it, never fail silently, and do not advance. Tap/text path: a toast "Couldn't save that, tap to retry" and the picked tiles stay selected for the retry. Voice path: one short coach line "That didn't go through, let me try again." (Yair-approved tool-failure contract, 2026-07-09.)`,voice:"clip-family:onboard_goals_energy_edge_1 (pending recording)"},{edge:"off-topic input",behavior:'one short acknowledgement, at most one sentence, no new topic and no advice, then re-ask the goal question ("Which of these feels right to start with?"). Do not follow the tangent, do not add commentary, do not advance.',voice:"clip-family:onboard_goals_energy_edge_2 (pending recording)"},{edge:"skip / decline",behavior:"user will not choose: falls to the plain one-line re-ask and the tap path (max-turns behavior, no brainstorm; copy-decisions 2026-07-10), never force a pick"},{edge:"empty state",behavior:'no tiles appeared for the user: ask one neutral question ("Is anything coming up for you to pick from?"), do NOT recite the goal list to fill the silence',voice:"clip-family:onboard_goals_energy_edge_4 (pending recording)"},{edge:"names three",behavior:"ask which two matter most, then take those two"},{edge:'vague / general ("just more energy in general")',behavior:'map to the closest label or ask one short question to pin it ("If you had to pick one, what bothers you most?"); never invent a label',voice:"clip-family:onboard_goals_energy_edge_6 (pending recording)"}],enforcedBy:["eval:edge-walk"]},acceptance:{rows:[{criterion:"shows the right thing",check:"phone renders goals-list for Feel more energized, 3 tiles + create-your-own, multi-select 1-2, nothing preselected (diff phone vs components)"},{criterion:"says the right thing",check:"opener spoken verbatim, category named once, no read / praise / contrarian / platitude (rules.context evals)"},{criterion:"advances correctly",check:"one or two goals captured via submit_goals, then advance_step; a three-goal attempt resolves to two first (flow gate)"},{criterion:"survives a refresh",check:"goals + count persist, beat not re-asked, current_step resumes past goals-energy (persistence resume key)"},{criterion:"routes correctly",check:"each picked goal routes to its matching habits-* opener; the goal count sets the downstream habit distribution"}],enforcedBy:["component-registry-check","advance-gate-check","persistence-contract-check","render-link-integrity-check","eval:parity-walk","eval:edge-walk"]},applicableDecisions:{rows:[{decision:"4/5. Habit cap (2 habits total, floor 1, distributable: 2 goals x1 or 1 goal x2)",binds:!1,how:"not enforced on this beat; the cap is enforced on the downstream habits beat. This goals beat captures the 1-or-2 goal COUNT that decision 4/5 uses to distribute the cap, so it is the input, not the gate."},{decision:"1, 2 (profile gates), 3 (women-art), 6, 7 (reflection)",binds:!1,how:"not this beat"}],enforcedBy:["decisions-coverage-check"]},sectionManifest:{identity:"derived",scriptMeta:"derived",components:"derived",voice:"derived",rulesContext:"derived",rulesCode:"derived",conversation:"derived",contextProse:"derived",allowedTools:"derived",persistence:"derived",flow:"derived",edges:"derived",acceptance:"derived",applicableDecisions:"derived"}},io:{dataIn:[{key:"onboarding.category",from:"flow-state",writtenBy:"submit_category"}],dataOut:[{key:"onboarding.goals",from:"flow-state",writtenBy:"submit_goals",persistsTo:"onboarding_states.data (verify key)",note:"goal count = goals.length, DERIVED (drives the habits distribution); not a separate persisted field"}]},spokenContent:"Within that, what's the piece you want to start with?",openerShowsAsBubble:!0},{id:"onboarding-beginner-beat-12-pick-goals:stress",name:"Goals (Reduce stress)",order:17,path:"beginner",type:"goals-list",context:`BEAT: Goals.
