     1	// Guard 2 of 2: LINK INTEGRITY.
     2	// Every script line must point at something real:
     3	//   1. bindsTo.element must resolve within that beat entry's own element
     4	//      vocabulary. A component line that names a declared elementId (e.g. "age",
     5	//      "sleep", "createOwn") must have that id in the beat's declared elements;
     6	//      structural tokens the script itself owns (bubble-N, opener, reveal-N,
     7	//      close-bubble, second-bubble, confirm-bubble, opener-line) are valid.
     8	//      A line pointing at an element the beat does not declare fails.
     9	//   2. every clip id must resolve to a real file under public/voice (the /voice/ob
    10	//      clips plus the splash welcome). A line with a clip that has no file fails.
