    32	| `eval:edge-walk` (74) | **NOT-IMPLEMENTED** | None found in all three scopes | No harness evaluator walks all edges/branches or asserts stated outcomes. `advanceStep` validates a subset of forward state transitions, not render edge coverage. | Nowhere. |
