    36	| `eval:verbatim-opener` (58) | **NOT-IMPLEMENTED** | **No implementation found anywhere** | No repo/app/spec evaluator compares an emitted opener to a required verbatim string. The app parity test merely rejects em dashes/gesture words in configured openers (`beat-context-parity.test.ts:88`); that is not verbatim matching. | Nowhere. |
