    44	
    45	## Yair’s specific questions
    46	
    47	### 1. Rule-ID prefixes: complete beat-by-beat map
    48	
    49	The rule prefix is a local namespace for the specific beat or variant, **not** an enforcement implementation selector. The complete prefix→beat map extracted from `rulesCode[].id` is:
    50	
    51	| Prefix | Beat namespace |
    52	|---|---|
    53	| `greet` | `onboarding-beat-3-coach-greeting` |
    54	| `signup` | `onboarding-beat-4-sign-up` |
